plot: A new villain, Kilovolt, attacks the new community center, and Angelique gives up names in Forbes' assassination.

As Batwoman focuses even more effort on taking down Black Mask, a new foe emerges, diverting the Bat Team's attention to a distressing issue in Gotham. Continually haunted by the mistakes of his past, Jacob travels down a dangerous path in an attempt to eradicate them. Alice and Julia discover they have an enemy in common.—The CW
